Fri Oct 27 12:04:17 2000  Chris Cleeland  <cleeland_c@ociweb.com>

        * platform_chorus.GNU:
        * platform_chorus4.x_g++.GNU:
        * platform_chorus_ghs.GNU:
        * platform_cray.GNU:
