          - ACE_HAS_STRCASECMP_EQUIVALENT
          - ACE_HAS_STRNCASECMP_EQUIVALENT
          - ACE_ITOA_EQUIVALENT

          These are used to specify different names for functions
          that differ in names across different compilers.

